(6278,	1180,	'hotel_discount',	'As many of our delegates travel from all over the UK & Ireland we have negotiated a special discount if you would like to stay in the hotel while the course is on. Please call us and we can help arrange this for you.'),
(6279,	1180,	'address',	'Hilton Hyde Park<br>\r\n129 Bayswater Road<br>\r\nLondon<br>\r\nW2 4RJ<br>\r\n'),
(6280,	1180,	'by_rail',	'&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Mainline</strong>\r\n<br><br>\r\nLondon Paddington station is approximately 0.8 miles (15 minute walk) from the hotel.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Underground (Tube)</strong>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Option 1: </strong>Take the Central line to Queensway. When you leave the station, turn tight onto Bayswater Road and you will see the hotel immediately.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>Option 2:</strong> Take the Circle or Disctrict Line to Bayswater station. Take a right when you leave the station and walk to Bayswater Road. Take a right at the junction and you will see the hotel on your right.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you are planning to travel by public transport you should check the Transport for London (TFL) website a few days before the course, for planned engineering works and track closures.'),
(6281,	1180,	'by_car',	'Parking is limited around the hotel but Q-Park Queensway do offer discounted rates on weekends. Roughly £24 for 2 days (weekend only) parking when booked in advance.\r\n<br><br>\r\nSimply Enter the Postcode into your SatNav and it should bring you straight to the venue - W2 4RJ, no. 129.\r\n<br><br>\r\nNote: You can park for free on Sundays on Baywater Road on single yellow lines. NOT Saturdays though. Please check with Westminster Council for further details as restrictions can vary.'),
