(25,	1,	'2015-01-31 13:17:54',	'2015-01-31 13:17:54',	'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/aboutus.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1666\" src=\"http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/aboutus.gif\" alt=\"aboutus\" width=\"800\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>“To be the UK’s leading provider of quality technology and management training”</strong></p>\r\nWe are the UK\'s leading IT training provider. Our wealth of industry experience and ability to attract the best instructors allows us to deliver the highest quality training at the most competitive prices.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>How do we achieve our mission?</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe offer weekend courses in central London locations so that you can still get the training you need without taking time off work. Our experienced trainers will give you all the tools you need to successfully pass the courses and allow you to take your career to the next level.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Core Values</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We perform to the highest standards for all of our customers</li>\r\n	<li>We only employ the highest calibre trainers to ensure that our customers needs can be fully met.</li>\r\n	<li>We believe in environmental sustainability and as such we are always seeking to reduce our carbon footprint.</li>\r\n	<li>We do our best to manage our business on a clear and consistent set of Business Principles.</li>\r\n	<li>We treat all of our colleagues with respect. We strongly believe that different perspectives and experiences leads to the development of the best training and development solutions for our customers.</li>\r\n</ul>',	'About Us',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'about-us',	'',	'',	'2015-03-21 23:16:23',	'2015-03-21 23:16:23',	'',	0,	'http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/?page_id=25',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
