(1690,	1,	'2015-03-22 14:01:42',	'2015-03-22 14:01:42',	'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/inhouse-mainpage.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1645\" src=\"http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/inhouse-mainpage.gif\" alt=\"inhouse-mainpage\" width=\"800\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\nOur onsite tailor-made training solutions are well suited to those clients who wish to have personalised content and delivery to enhance the business benefits for their delegates. We are happy to collaborate with you to design a solution specific to your needs.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWe offer a range of flexible in-house training options for small, medium and large businesses as well as individuals. Our corporate training involves providing personal, tailored and flexible options for you and your organisation. We can train and certify individuals, teams or even entire departments. We will help you define a strategy for Learning and Development within your organisation to ensure your employees are trained to the highest levels. There are a number of advantages of having teams trained in-house rather than sending staff on individual training courses: \r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Trainer — consistent teaching style and delivery to avoid confusion </li> \r\n<li>Consistency — working off the same set of assumptions, concepts and terminology </li> \r\n<li>Relevant — specific and relevant examples for your organisation, rather than general examples </li> \r\n<li>Tailored — Focused and tailored content based on the level and knowledge of your staff</li>\r\n<li>Team Building — allows teams to collaborate and work together on problem solving exercises</li>\r\n<li>Flexibility — you choose the dates and times of the training</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you have groups of four or more then in-house training can really make the most of your training budget and allow you to up-skill a lot more staff. The more students the greater the cost savings per head. \r\n<br><br>\r\nWe have worked with some of the largest institutions in the world, delivering our training and consultancy services in a number of different countries around the world, Read Our-Clients section for more details. \r\n<br><br>\r\nGet in touch and we will devise the perfect strategy for your training needs: \r\n',	'In-House Training',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'1352-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-03-22 14:01:42',	'2015-03-22 14:01:42',	'',	1352,	'http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/1352-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
