(1646,	1,	'2015-03-21 21:39:16',	'2015-03-21 21:39:16',	'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/inhouse-mainpage.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1645\" src=\"http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/inhouse-mainpage.gif\" alt=\"inhouse-mainpage\" width=\"800\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\nOur onsite tailor-made training solutions are well suited to those clients who wish to have personalised content and delivery to enhance the business benefits for their delegates. We are happy to collaborate with you to design a solution specific to your needs.\r\n\r\nBenefits of onsite training:\r\nAllow us to design bespoke tailor-made content for your environment, making learning more relevant.\r\nDelivering training on your site reduces on travel costs.\r\nChoice of dates that suit your organisation - making the delivery more convenient for you.\r\nBy delivering onsite training more staff can benefit, to gain the maximum ROI.\r\nTraining demonstrates a real commitment to staff performance improvement and increases staff motivation',	'In-House Training',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'1352-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-03-21 21:39:16',	'2015-03-21 21:39:16',	'',	1352,	'http://www.bluerhinotraining.com/1352-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
